Schmidt May Propose Steinbruck as Chancellor Nominee, Bild Says

-- B y   S h e e n a g h   M a t t h e w s
-- 
2011-10-23T12:45:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-23/schmidt-may-propose-steinbruck-as-chancellor-nominee-bild-says.html
Former German Chancellor Helmut Schmidt may propose  Peer Steinbrueck  as chancellor candidate for
the opposition  Social Democratic Party  during a TV talk-show
appearance tonight, Bild said.  Steinbrueck, a former finance minister, will appear with
Schmidt on a show hosted by Guenther Jauch to talk about the
financial crisis, the German newspaper said. Steinbrueck is
campaigning internally against Sigmar Gabriel and Frank-Walter Steinmeier, the newspaper said.  Steinbrueck has written a paper for the SPD on the euro
crisis in an effort to show that he can lead in a crisis, Bild
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sheenagh Matthews in Frankfurt at 
 smatthews6@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
